    <td width="100%"><b><font face="Verdana" size="2"><span class="arial221">
    <span style="color: #CC0000">Movers Arena</span></span><br>
    Movers Arena is a source for moving estimates (leads) using the Pay per 
    Estimate method. <br>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Pay per Estimate</span></span><br>
    The 
    moving company selects the desired estimates after reviewing important 
    information regarding the estimates; origin, destination, date of move, job 
    volume, items list, estimate price, how many time the estimate was bought 
    etc; and then purchase that estimate.<br>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Pricing</span></span><br>
    Each estimate has its own price and the buyer sees that price before he or 
    she buy it. For example; a Long Distance estimate can cost between $6 
    to $8 on a shared base and 
    an exclusive estimate can cost between $12 to $15.<br>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Auto Purchase (Option 
    one)<br>
    </span></span>Select a working area which estimates from that region will be 
    automatically transferred into your personal account. By assigning a primary 
    zip code and a radius of operation, you will receive <font color="#CE0000">
    two estimates</font> for the price of one estimate. That is a significant 
    price reduction!!!<br><br>
