</font></b><p><span class="arial221"><b>
    <font face="Verdana" size="2" color="#CC0000">Manual Purchase</font></b></span><b><font face="Verdana" size="2"><span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000"> 
    (Option two)</span></span><br>
    This method allows the mover to purchase only the estimates that he or she 
    selects. <br>
    Movers Arena has created affordable plans which cut the price of the 
    estimates.<br>
    When depositing any amount from the following table you will get the relative 
    bonus.</font></b></p>
