    <p><b><font face="Verdana" size="2">&nbsp;<br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Electronic Estimates</span></span><span style="color: #CC0000"><span class="arial221"><br>
    </span></span>All the estimates are stored in a secured personal database. 
    When you sign up (for free) with Movers Arena you will receive&nbsp; username 
    and password&nbsp; and a 
    link to your personal account.&nbsp; </font>
    <span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Verdana">Also, $12 
    complimentary credit will be posted to your account.</span><font face="Verdana" size="2"><br>
    <br>
    <span style="color: #CC0000">
    <span class="arial221">
    Sharing Estimates</span></span><br>
    The shared estimates can be sold up to five companies.
    <span style="color: #CC0000"> <span class="arial221">
    Period! <br>
    </span> </span>The system always notifies how many times the estimate was 
    taken (zero to four times).<br>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Exclusive Estimates</span></span><br>
    When an estimate has not been sold yet (&quot;taken&quot; is zero), the buyer has the option 
    to purchase that estimate exclusively. Meaning, only the buyer will get this 
    estimate.<br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000"><br>
    Refund Policy </span></span></font></b><br>
    <b><font face="Verdana" size="2">We are doing the best to filter junk 
    estimates with false information. <br>
    However, the system cannot stop all fake estimates. Therefore we credit 
    these bogus&nbsp; transactions.<span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000"><br>
    <br>
    Favorites Service</span></span><br>
    The system notifies you on new estimates that fit your needs. The 
    estimates are being sent immediately over the email when they entered the system. This priority service gives you the 
    opportunity to be number-one buyer. <br>
    Alter your <a href="http://www.moversarena.com/wc.dll?mpreposit~arenain~XXX~<%=ALLT(pcCUSTNO)%>~RULESWC~?<%=SYS(2015)%>">favorites</a>.<br>
    <br>
    <span class="arial221"><span style="color: #CC0000">Affiliates</span></span><br>
    Movers Arena is affiliated with the following companies:<br>
    GRANOT, INC. -  Online Moving System<br>
    Relocations Network Media Group - Moving Directory<br>
    5 Star Movers - Moving Directory<br>
    Moving411 - Moving Directory<br>
    Moving Discount - Moving Directory</font></b></p>
    <p><b><font face="Verdana" size="2">
